is the best <normalised orig="recompence" auto="true">recompense</normalised> we can make to our Blessed <lb/>
Saviour for all his pains and sufferings. When <lb/>
                  <quote type="biblical" ana="Isa 53.10">the pleasure of the Lord prospers in his hand</quote> by the conversion <lb/>
