<normalised orig="easie" auto="true">easy</normalised> and his burden light</quote>, Matt. 11. 30. Gods service is <lb/>
perfect freedom, as we daily stile it in our prayers. And <lb/>
                  <quote type="biblical" ana="1 Jn 5.3">his commandments are not grievous</quote>, 1 Joh. 5. 3. Shall we <lb/>
