as much his wisdom as it is to go <normalised orig="cloathed" auto="true">clothed</normalised> in decent <lb/>
Apparel, and to eat and drink what is good for his <lb/>
nourishment. But on the other hand, for one to run <lb/>
naked about the Streets, to fill his mouth with mire and <lb/>
